  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-02-23",
    "date": "2021-03-29T13:46:17Z",
    "text": "End College Chinese Communist Partnerships Act or the End College CCP Act\n\nThis bill generally prohibits an institution of higher education (IHE) from receiving federal funds if the IHE has a contractual partnership with the Chinese government or an entity that is organized under the laws of China. An IHE may regain eligibility for federal funds by disclosing and terminating those contractual partnerships."
  },
